## Testing Search

```ruby
test "searches articles" do
  visit articles_url
  
  fill_in "Search", with: "Ruby"
  click_button "Search"
  
  assert_selector ".article", count: 2
  assert_text "Ruby on Rails"
  assert_no_text "Python Tutorial"
end
```

